"Zamuti levy kanal puvodni video audio stopy." = "Mutes the left channel of the original video audio track.";
"Zamuti pravy kanal puvodni video audio stopy." = "Mutes the right channel of the original video audio track.";
"Zapina nebo vypina celou audio stopu z videa." = "Enables or disables the entire video audio track.";
"Zapina nebo vypina importovanou externi audio stopu." = "Enables or disables the imported external audio track.";
"Kdyz je ON, v seznamu replik se zobrazi jen repliky bez charakteru." = "When ON, only lines without a character are shown in the line list.";
"Aplikuje offset jen na prehravani videa." = "Applies offset to video playback only.";
"Aplikuje offset na vsechny repliky, nebo jen na vybrane pri vice-vyberu." = "Applies offset to all lines, or only to selected lines when multiple are selected.";
"Pouzije se pro akci 'Vytvorit a odeslat mailem'. Muze obsahovat i vice adres oddelenych carkou." = "Used for the 'Create and Send by Email' action. May contain multiple addresses separated by commas.";
"Smaze vybrane repliky (Delete/Backspace)" = "Deletes selected lines (Delete/Backspace)";
"Posune textove timecody o zadanou hodnotu. Kdyz je vybrano vice replik, aplikuje se jen na vybrane." = "Shifts text timecodes by the given value. When multiple lines are selected, applies only to the selection.";
"Posune video vuci timecodum. Hodnota + znamena, ze video pujde pozdeji." = "Shifts video against timecodes. A positive value means video will play later.";

